Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:35.93,ScreenWord,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\be10\1a&H60&\3a&H30&\fsp8}人类军Poliʻahu运输基地 上空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是皆城总士
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当你听到这段话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我想必已经不在这个世上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,二十二世纪对人类来说 成为了战争的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来自遥远宇宙的未知存在 Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有超越人知之力的它们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,已出现在这个星球四十年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,世界的大半都化为战场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,进入战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,距离降下还有60秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,全员 准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.60,0:01:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,服从作战 迅速加入前线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.44,0:01:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.52,0:01:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,发射台 固定完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,接收诱导信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,发射轨道 无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.49,0:01:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Aloha Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,基斯的话 真有可能向敌人搭讪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我还真想被搭讪呢 被金色的外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都是完成了严酷训练
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,存活至今的精锐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,能和你们并肩作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,二号机 上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,比报告中还要糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}二号机 Olympia-Angels
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}着陆确认
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要像哥哥一样战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧 比利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,四号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,五号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,六号机 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对Festum专用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,思维控制 体感操控式有人兵器法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(927,654)\fs35}Fafner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只有被选中之人才能操纵的 我们的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Type1 2 3 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.06,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,注意Type4
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,内藏敌人的一部分 将其力量为人类所用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,若不是法芙娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想必早就被毁灭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就算距离胜利尚远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,却争取到了抱有希望的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,莫甘机呼叫哥鲁德队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始加入前线
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 不要通信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,暗号联络全都被读取了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,上层太小看敌人的读心能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会被敌人读心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,冒纳基火山警戒基地陷落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,全部功能都被敌人夺取了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧让平民避难 全体部队向北端集结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,第一防卫队 全灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.24,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,距离大岛最终防卫线还有2公里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请避难 纳雷因将军
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.08,0:05:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是太平洋圈最大的运输基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里一旦陷落 数百万人会活活饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何都要守住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,先前明明不屑一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是学到人类怎样保命了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Festum
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能登机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那些家伙已经来到附近了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,冒纳基没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,十号机 严重损毁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,乔治被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不要停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,按照作战前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,发现哥鲁德队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,艾！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.90,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是敌人 被敌人同化了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,麦克 切断罗武的右臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\an8}罗武 快脱离 罗武
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,该死 进到心里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,罗武… 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,无法脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,芬里尔 起动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(604,653.333)}Fenrir
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我还能战斗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,罗武！ 罗武！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 哥哥 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.20,0:08:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,比利！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那是 什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,光弘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,光弘！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,总部发动交战规定α
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,对象是大岛全域
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,总部指挥的轰炸部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.34,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,给我接新联合国总部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以我的名义下达攻击中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人侵入基地内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,民间运输机被击坠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有同伴在战斗呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有几万的平民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,交战规定α要绝对服从
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快收回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,剥夺沃尔特少校的权限 逮捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,纳雷因将军发出中止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已经迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,输入坐标 准备攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢把同伴给…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以 将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,全体人员搜寻幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sphinx型…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 向同伴开枪了… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了 呐 还有人活着吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 凭我们是赢不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是为何而战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 究竟是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,世界因长期战乱而疲惫不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果能相互理解对方的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这场战争是否也会终结呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这一缕微弱的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,正要诞生在世界一隅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:50.92,ScreenWord,,0,0,0,,{\fad(840,1170)\be5\1a&H80&\3a&H30&\fsp8\pos(644,710)}龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,龙宫岛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,日本在战乱中毁灭后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:16:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为了留下和平文化而建造的人工岛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是我曾经的居所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,地区对抗赛快到啦 加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,美三香遵命 要老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,美三香 你就不要较真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了咲良 有人受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,让她们休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,继续继续
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,请了请了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,看到那孩子 就会想起从前的一骑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.25,0:17:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,从前的… 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.86,0:17:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 回去的时候要去一骑那里吃个饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不喜欢吃我做的菜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 不是那样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.86,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}高拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}堂马广登特别节目 追踪谜之巨大生物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,到底做了多少节目啊 笨蛋广登
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,芹也太惯着他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,闲着无聊 又热得难受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 我想去亚尔维斯工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(712,655)}Alvis
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要净学些打打杀杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你也要继承岛上的文化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那至少开空调啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,中… 中午好 里奈前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事 镝木
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你昨天也买了这个来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,呃… 买来保存用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,鏑木 你是学生会长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道买漫画 七夕祭的准备完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.98,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,里奈前辈不在 议程都没进展
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}下次要在一骑前辈那里一起开会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.72,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}是… 是 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 里奈前辈 待会儿有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我在工作哦 怎么可能有空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是这个劲头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,比起设计机体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.38,0:19:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,更要学习实际组装的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,六号改 腕部驱动系统 组装完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(387,653)}Mark Sechs
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,请进行FTP试验
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,确认连接
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,变熟练了呢 卡农
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有妈妈教我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里是乘员兼教官哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 出来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,一整天憋在那里会生病的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还想去一骑那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我去哪里都无所谓…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已经不想让任何人搭乘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,结果又要组装这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,卡农居然会修习工程师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那么年轻 技术却很是了得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还说想向保先生求教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我该退休了吧 还要继续做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.54,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是驾驶员培养教材吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不好说 西尾老师拜托的不好拒绝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该吃饭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那就还是吃咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还没好吗 赶不上午餐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,御门来啦 搬到里面去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,总是麻烦你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对 爸爸教的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,比起这个 一骑先生 有客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,总士 好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,上午的研究结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看来还在准备 我待会儿再来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.16,0:21:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧 工作餐不介意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是晖咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 新商品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 但是以制作人的名字命名的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里的规矩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一骑咖喱什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.74,0:22:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是沟口先生擅自取的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.62,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然很尊敬一骑前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,远见和沟口先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,在天上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,最近一直都是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,本以为能和远见前辈一起工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrows呼叫指挥中心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尾随不明机 输入导弹诱导装置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.92,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大小姐不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这个又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,锁定 发射导弹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(640,650)}Target Fox-One
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫Arrows 你追超了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行 不能因为飞得快 就追过敌人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.98,0:23:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,又输给沟口先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.42,0:23:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要是实战的话被击坠的就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace 请求继续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,OK Arrows 再次带头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(772,652)}Lead again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,收到 老爹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40}Wilco: Will comply
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.58,0:23:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(590,655)}Wilco
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.96,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个称呼就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,坐在大飞机上啊 不怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽真是的 最近总是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.86,0:23:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和空想的朋友对话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.44,0:23:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为没有其他同龄孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她是个感性丰富的孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.22,0:24:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不论如何都会不放心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真矢姐姐也坐在飞机上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.78,0:24:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就快了呢 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.06,0:24:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,味道如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.98,0:24:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很是稀松平常
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.36,0:24:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.02,0:24:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我来教你什么叫料理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,比预定的高了整整两度 需要修正
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.30,0:24:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真是死脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.72,0:24:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,两个午餐套餐是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.50,0:25:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两个咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.84,0:25:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.66,0:25:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这是皆城炖汤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.78,0:25:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我没点啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.22,0:25:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很好喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,午安
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.14,0:25:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,全是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.90,0:25:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么连总士都…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.24,0:25:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,卡农是冰淇淋蜜瓜苏打和 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.64,0:25:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 我没有点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.32,0:25:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,赠品 因为你是老主顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.14,0:25:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.20,0:25:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,…不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.10,0:25:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩30次
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.10,0:25:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,下次检查是下周呢 别忘了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.44,0:25:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.64,0:25:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的成人仪式也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.60,0:25:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要来帮忙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.86,0:25:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一直以来多谢了 剑司
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:25:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那拜拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.64,0:26:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.12,0:26:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,先是我 然后又关心一骑的身体？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.14,0:26:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.34,0:26:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,总是关心别人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.08,0:26:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是也做点自己喜欢的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.76,0:26:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我有在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.10,0:26:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,和你一起吃饭什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.04,0:26:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.90,0:26:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,远见是航空 卡农是工学
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.30,0:26:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,剑司是医疗 要是教育
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.72,0:26:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都决定了前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.68,0:26:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,总士是研究吗 感觉很合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢 在咖啡店做料理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.98,0:26:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到还挺适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.80,0:26:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要活用原王牌驾驶员的宝贵经验的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.54,0:26:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以做教官
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.48,0:26:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不驾驶法芙娜也不会消失呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.20,0:26:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是尼伯龙根连接造成的小规模同化现象
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.20,0:26:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(401,652)}Nibelung
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天会找到治愈方法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.76,0:27:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,学点什么 尝试做点什么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.86,0:27:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不想让它成为未完的遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.64,0:27:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是这样吗 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.64,0:27:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,恢复的可能性是有的 不要太悲观
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.98,0:27:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.32,0:27:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有三年
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.34,0:27:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么长的时间 足够做觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.42,0:27:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 眼睛也能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.28,0:27:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里生活安稳 又有重要的伙伴在
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.30,0:27:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.70,0:27:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,总士前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要去下层区域吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.40,0:27:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,去生物圈研究所之前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.62,0:27:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想看看乙姬的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.36,0:27:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,立上是医师方向吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.88,0:27:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,转成特殊医疗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.00,0:28:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,远见大夫说要照顾乙姬的话 两边都需要
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.58,0:28:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.90,0:28:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.72,0:28:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,比起乙姬做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.72,0:28:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.96,0:28:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在外面的世界 战斗还在继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.86,0:28:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,根据所罗门的回应
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,战火反而扩大了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.86,0:28:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,乙姬明明那么希望和平
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.40,0:28:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.20,0:29:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.70,0:29:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你一直守护着岛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.82,0:29:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 出什么事了 乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.42,0:29:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是对什么做出反应了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗指挥中心 不明机接近
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.96,0:29:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs38\pos(501,650)}C D C
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.78,0:29:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,90秒后到达护罩圈
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.62,0:29:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,目标进入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.22,0:29:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,目标 交汇
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.50,0:29:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,照会 C-300 Super Galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.96,0:29:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类军的大型运输机
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.90,0:29:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,人类军…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.06,0:30:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能感觉到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.98,0:30:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.06,0:30:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,在非常美丽的岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.82,0:30:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,艾梅莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.54,0:30:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,将军
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.00,0:30:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,艾梅莉似乎也感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.78,0:30:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不想让我们相见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.60,0:30:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace呼叫战斗指挥中心 紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.92,0:30:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrows 在射程范围内跟踪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.46,0:30:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.56,0:30:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,奶奶 我去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,报告状况
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.74,0:31:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,演习中的Kestrel报告
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.02,0:31:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,人类军运输机接近中 发生紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.68,0:31:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,护罩圈外确认质量不明的Worm
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.00,0:31:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,所罗门尚无回应
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.12,0:31:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,全区域转入迎击态势
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.08,0:31:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,第一 第二重力波护罩展开完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.08,0:31:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(649,656)}Welle Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.00,0:31:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,航向不变 法芙娜待机 不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.64,0:31:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人还没有发现岛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.34,0:31:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只是人类军被追击
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.50,0:31:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样坐视不理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.04,0:31:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,居住区请求通信 是日野家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.58,0:31:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,接过来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.52,0:31:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.40,0:31:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}求你啦 妈妈 求你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.52,0:31:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,美羽她突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.30,0:31:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}没事的美羽 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.04,0:31:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是 说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.08,0:31:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}现在正拜托对面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.48,0:31:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,救救那架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.48,0:31:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}今天预定出勤的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.18,0:31:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}请马上紧急出动进入待机状态
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.86,0:31:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}各位岛民请避免外出 等待最新情报
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.96,0:31:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}伴随紧急出动状态 第一…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.34,0:31:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,高拜果然棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.26,0:31:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,彗 昨天你也买了一样的杂志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.56,0:31:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.81,0:31:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(706,208)\fnSimHei\b1\frx2\fry346\frz19.01}播报出击请求
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.02,0:31:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\pos(531,94)}Waffenlager
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.02,0:31:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}隔离墙起动准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.54,0:32:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}向岛防卫线 刚瑠岛工区 庆树岛区…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.72,0:31:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,变成出击请求了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.24,0:32:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.24,0:32:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的摄影照明差强人意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.82,0:32:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.68,0:32:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不陪你折腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.10,0:32:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也能乘上法芙娜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.28,0:32:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,连接测试都没做？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.22,0:32:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,只是观战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.16,0:32:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没像广登前辈那样做头盔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.96,0:32:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.40,0:32:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}即将抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.18,0:32:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.40,0:32:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我从前辈那里继承的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.22,0:32:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好珍惜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.80,0:32:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,广登前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.34,0:32:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.84,0:32:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\an8}抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.78,0:32:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好帅气…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.50,0:32:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗 把护身符送人了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.42,0:32:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能驾驶法芙娜的时间也没几年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.30,0:32:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,得趁现在传下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.22,0:33:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,将军…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.52,0:33:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能主动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.40,0:33:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,找到我们了…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.06,0:33:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所罗门回应 200秒以内敌人实体化的可能性很大
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.46,0:33:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,方向50 速度减慢 护罩部分解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.34,0:33:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Kestrel诱导运输机水面降落
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.58,0:33:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,战斗指挥中心呼叫Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.26,0:33:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请按照规定开始诱导
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.24,0:33:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.28,0:33:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,伪装镜面 解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.44,0:33:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,输入密码 伪装镜面解除
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.94,0:33:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是岛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.70,0:33:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 存在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.84,0:33:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,果然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.78,0:33:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.70,0:34:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,毕业考试来了 交给你了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.54,0:34:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.64,0:34:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫飞行中的C-300
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.30,0:34:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是FA3 代号「Arrows」 请回应
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.18,0:34:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢通信
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.12,0:34:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是C-300 代号「海兽」
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.12,0:34:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\fnArial\pos(826,654)}kētos
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.36,0:34:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,人类军南亚舰队所属 特殊航空连队 珀尔修斯中队
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.48,0:34:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫海兽 请遵从诱导
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.40,0:34:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫Arrows 全面服从
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.18,0:34:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,相对的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.02,0:34:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,请转达贵方的指挥者
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.96,0:34:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我方希望让双方的希望相见
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.78,0:34:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,希望…？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.62,0:35:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,付出大量牺牲赢得的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.42,0:35:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,即使失去它 也要追求的是何物
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.08,0:35:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,未知的希望 与新的战斗一并来访的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后的时间 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.32,0:35:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,苍穹之法芙娜 EXODUS第二集
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.78,0:35:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\1c&H373A1B&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\b1\pos(924,550)}希望之{\r\1c&H2B1998&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\b1}名{\r\1c&H373A1B&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\b1}为
